title: 30 Seconds to Mars - Acoustic 2005
description:
Artist: 30 Seconds to Mars
Album: Acoustic
Release year: 2005

---------------------------------------------------
30 Seconds to Mars (or Thirty Seconds to Mars and 
often abbreviated to 30STM) is a rock band from Los 
Angeles, California, featuring actor Jared Leto as 
the lead vocalist, guitarist & songwriter.
---------------------------------------------------

This Bundle is a collection of acoustic live and
nonlive tracks: 

Capricorn (Live)
Echelon (Live)
A Modern myth (Live)
From Yesterday (Live)
The Kill (Solo)
The Kill (Live)
The Story
Was it a dream (Live)
Message in a bottle (Police Cover)
